acy as\nthe non-pulsating case. These results can be used in many applications, e.g.,\nto predict/constrain properties of planetary systems orbiting white dwarfs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2013 18:37:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
