le combination based on pairwise maximization of similarity is as\neffective as a non-trivial optimization of parameters. Our approach is fully\nautomatic, unsupervised, and scalable for real-time detection of memes in\nstreaming data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 10 Oct 2013 00:10:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-07"}
